    "projectUrl": "https://github.com/robinrodricks/FluentFTP",
    "description": "An FTP and FTPS client for .NET & .NET Standard, optimized for speed. Provides extensive FTP commands, File uploads/downloads, SSL/TLS connections, Directory listing parsing, File hashing/checksums, File permissions/CHMOD, FTP proxies, FXP transfers, UTF-8 support, Async/await support, Powershell support and more. Written entirely in C#, with no external dependencies.",
    "license": "LICENSE.TXT",
    "tags": "ftp,ftp-client,ftps,ssl,tls,unix,iis",
